@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@workflowId = task-http-workflow

### 1. HTTP 노드 워크플로우 저장
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{workflowId}}",
  "name": "HTTP Node Runtime Test",
  "version": 1,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "node_start",
      "name": "Start",
      "type": "START",
      "params": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "node_http",
      "name": "HTTP Request",
      "type": "HTTP",
      "params": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://httpbin.org/anything/orders/<<order.id>>",
        "headers": {
          "X-Tenant-Id": "<<tenantId>>"
        },
        "queryParams": {
          "include": "details",
          "requestId": "<<requestId>>"
        },
        "body": {
          "status": "<<order.status>>"
        },
        "timeoutMillis": 3000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node_done",
      "name": "Done",
      "type": "END",
      "params": {
        "name": "HTTP flow completed"
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "node_start": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "nodeId": "node_http",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "node_http": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "nodeId": "node_done",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  }
}

### 2. 워크플로우 실행
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/executions/{{workflowId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "tenant-1",
  "requestId": "req-9",
  "order": {
    "id": "ord-1",
    "status": "PAID"
  }
}

> {% client.global.set("httpExecutionId", response.body.executionId); %}

### 3. 실행 상태 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/executions/{{httpExecutionId}}

### 4. 노드 실행 이력 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/executions/{{httpExecutionId}}/nodes
